---
title: Cheesy Pizza with Garlicky Mushrooms and Tomato Rocket Salad
description: Looking for a tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Cheesy Pizza with Mushrooms and Salad in just 20 minutes for a balanced and tasty dinnertime.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cheesy-pizza-af6244d0-459d3766.jpg
